  <part xml:id="user.manual">
    <title>OpenEngSB Framework</title>
    <partintro>
      <para>This part gives an introduction into the OpenEngSB project and explains its base usage environment and the
        concepts, such as Domains, Connectors, Workflows and similar important ideas. Furthermore this part covers
